#. type: Bullet: '- '
msgid ""
"We had to temper several [[!wikipedia Denial-of-service_attack "
"desc=\"distributed denial-of-service (DDoS)\"]] attacks targeting our "
"infrastructure."
msgstr ""
"Hem hagut de temperar diversos atacs de [[!wikipedia_ca "
"Atac_de_denegació_de_servei desc=\"denegació de servei distribuïda (DDoS)\"]]"
" dirigits a la nostra infraestructura."

#. type: Bullet: '- '
msgid ""
"For 9 years, we have been relying on the hosting services provided by the "
"fine people of boum.org. Thank you! As they were reducing their activities, "
"we had to migrate our services. Our website is now self-hosted and our "
"mailing-lists are taken care of by 2 experienced and trusted autonomous "
"server projects: [autistici.org](https://autistici.org) and [puscii.nl]"
"(https://puscii.nl)."
msgstr ""
"Des de fa 9 anys, confiem en els serveis d'allotjament proporcionats per la "
"bona gent de boum.org. Gràcies! Com que anaven reduint les seves activitats, "
"vam haver de migrar els nostres serveis. El nostre lloc web ara està auto-"
"allotjat i les nostres llistes de correu estan gestionades per dos projectes "
"de servidors autònoms amb experiència i confiança: [autistici.org](https://"
"autistici.org) i [puscii.nl](https://puscii.nl)."

#. type: Title =
#, no-wrap
msgid "Community"
msgstr "Comunitat"

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"Over the years, Tails has been able to gather a lively community which is "
"growing, evolving, and deserves care."
msgstr ""
"Al llarg dels anys, Tails ha pogut reunir una comunitat animada que creix, "
"evoluciona i mereix atenció."

#. type: Bullet: '- '
msgid ""
"We published a statement of our [[mission and values|contribute/mission]] to "
"help us clarify who we are, what we stand for, and what we want to do for "
"our users."
msgstr ""
"Vam publicar una declaració de la nostra [[missió i valors|contribute/"
"mission]] per ajudar-nos a aclarir qui som, què defensem i què volem fer "
"pels nostres usuaris."

#. type: Bullet: '- '
msgid ""
"We agreed on [[user personas|contribute/personas]], fictitious but concrete "
"representations of the people using Tails. We use these personas to keep in "
"mind who we are working for, what are their needs, and what Tails should do "
"for them."
msgstr ""
"Vam acordar [[persones d'usuari|contribute/personas]], representacions "
"fictícies però concretes de les persones que utilitzen Tails. Utilitzem "
"aquestes persones per tenir en compte per a qui treballem, quines són les "
"seves necessitats i què hauria de fer Tails per elles."

#. type: Bullet: '- '
msgid ""
"We attended 9 conferences and connected to Free Software and Internet "
"freedom communities in 9 different countries, including FOSDEM (Belgium), "
"Internet Freedom Festival (Spain), Tor Meeting (Sweden), OTF Summit "
"(Taiwan), DebConf (Brazil), and MozFest (UK)."
msgstr ""
"Hem assistit a nou conferències i hem connectat amb programari lliure i "
"comunitats de llibertat d'Internet a nou països diferents, incloent FOSDEM "
"(Bèlgica), Internet Freedom Festival (Espanya), Tor Meeting (Suècia), OTF "
"Summit (Taiwan), DebConf (Brasil) i MozFest (Regne Unit)."

#. type: Bullet: '- '
msgid ""
"The wider Tails community organized 10 workshops to present Tails to new "
"users in North and South America, Europe, and East and South-East Asia."
msgstr ""
"La comunitat més àmplia de Tails va organitzar 10 tallers per presentar "
"Tails als nous usuaris d'Amèrica del Nord i del Sud, Europa i l'est i el sud-"
"est asiàtic."

#. type: Bullet: '- '
msgid ""
"We answered 883 bug reports through our help desk and helped all these "
"people to be safer online."
msgstr ""
"Hem contestat a 883 informes d'errors a través del nostre servei "
"d'assistència i hem ajudat a totes aquestes persones a estar més segures en "
"línia."

#. type: Plain text
msgid "- 2 new workers joined our help desk and sysadmin teams."
msgstr ""
"- Dos nous treballadors s'han unit al nostre servei d'ajuda i als equips "
"d'administració del sistema."

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"All of this is made possible by donations from people like you. And because "
"these help us to plan our work, we particularly appreciate monthly and "
"yearly donations, even the smallest ones."
msgstr ""
"Tot això és possible gràcies a les donacions de persones com tu. I com que "
"ens ajuden a planificar la nostra feina, agraïm especialment les donacions "
"mensuals i anuals, fins i tot les més petites."

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"If you liked our work in 2019, please take a minute to donate and make us "
"thrive in 2020!"
msgstr ""
"Si us ha agradat la nostra feina el 2019, preneu-vos un minut per fer una "
"donació i fer-nos prosperar el 2020!"

